Certainly! Here are some example sentences that use the Serbian word "ekipe" in different forms and positions:

1. Danas mi dolazi *ekipa* iz razreda. (*ekipa* - team, group) (Today, the *team* from my class is coming over to my place.)
2. Ova *ekipa* izgleda jako dobro na papiru. (*ekipa* - team, crew) (This *team* looks really good on paper.)
3. Hoćeš li doći na fudbal sa *ekipom*? (*ekipom* - with the team, group) (Will you come to play soccer with the *team*?)
4. Naša *ekipa* je pobedila na turniru. (*ekipa* - team, crew) (Our *team* won the tournament.)
5. Ova *ekipa* se ne slaže baš najbolje. (*ekipa* - team, crew) (This *team* doesn't really get along well.)
6. *Ekipa* je bila veoma zabavna sinoć. (*Ekipa* - crew, gang) (*The gang* was very fun last night.)
7. Molim vas da mi date više vremena, treba da skupim *ekipu*. (*ekipu* - team, group) (Please give me more time, I need to gather the *team*.)

I hope this helps!